          <p style="padding-top:10px">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
          <p>Welcome to XDS Spark! We are thrilled to provide you with login credentials that give access to your <b>complimentary</b>, Foundational membership.</p>
          <p>Click <a href="{{webSiteLoginUrl}}"><u>HERE</u></a> to access the log-in page. Your email is {{email}}, and your password is {{password}}</p>
          <p>As a Foundational member, you receive <b>full and unfettered access</b> to all features and functionality inside of Spark, including one (1) user account for yourself.</p>
          <p>Once you are logged in, here are a few tips to help you get started!</p>
          <ul>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Search for and View Basic Service Provider Profiles -</b> View rich Service Provider profiles including portfolios, project highlights, certification and due diligence info, events, and contacts.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Compare Service Providers -</b> Use the Compare feature to do side-by-side comparisons of multiple Service Providers in order to quickly view strengths and weaknesses.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Partner Relationship Management -</b> In a Service Provider profile, go to the <b>My Spark</b> tab to manage personalized information that <u>only you can see</u>.</li>
              <ul>
                <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Partner Status -</b> indicating the service providerâ€™s ability to work with your company</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Rates -</b> track day and monthly rates by service with notes, and post a rate card</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Performance -</b> track project performance by quality, on-time delivery and communication</li>
                <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Notes -</b> Post notes from meetings, or other important information on your partners</li>
              </ul>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Post Opportunities -</b> Use Post Opportunities to share an upcoming project in order to discover new Service Provider candidates. Your post can be <b>anonymous</b>, and will only be published to Service Providers whose skills match that of your needs.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Compare Service Providers -</b> Use the Compare feature to place up to 10 Service Providers side-by-side in order to evaluate strengths and gaps.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Follow Profiles -</b> Find a new Service Provider you find interesting? Hit the Follow button on their profile to receive weekly notifications when they update their profile.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>My Lists -</b> Build shareable lists of Service Providers any way you want, and track and maintain these over time. Copy a link to share lists with anyone in your organization, without the need for them to log in.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>My Projects -</b> Create projects and add lists of candidate Service Providers. Share projects with your teams to determine partners that are the best fit for engagements.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Events -</b> Interested in seeing which Service Providers will be at your next event? Use the Events filter to show a listing of partners you may want to meet with on site.</li>
          </ul>
